item.title: About
item.description: Eat This Radio is a platform for alternative music made by music lovers. We bring you mixes made by us, our friends and heroes. There is no regular schedule, we add new mixes when we get them. Check back on this website or follow us on Facebook Eat This Radio is made by: Bastiaan Verhage LN Wouter van Veldhoven With many thanks to: Michaala Jung Ingo Robhar
